FOR CONTINUOUS USE OF THE NOTIFIER ICON-
You can remove --listen from line 96 in: 
/usr/local/bin/tint2-apt-update-check
and then also place a line in ~/.config/openbox/autostart if desired:
tint2-apt-update-check &

/usr/local/bin/tint-2-apt-update-check  - main script
/usr/local/bin/tint-2-apt-update-check-color - for icon color
~/.config/tint2/executors/color.txt

And to call the main script:
/usr/share/lilidog/tint2/update-options
